Prompt — Build “Community Observer” Static Website
You are building a modern, static website for a local newspaper called Community
Observer.
Tech Stack & Hosting
1. Framework: Astro
2. Styling: Tailwind CSS (brand colors from masthead)
3. Hosting: Cloudflare Pages (Astro preset, build output to dist/)
